These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, gospel
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, surfing
There are 2 different favourite colors: pink, fuchsia
1. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
3. the fan of gospel is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes pink##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | house   |
| Sport         | surfing | cycling |
| Color     | pink | fuchsia    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: avocado, cabbage
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, documentary
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, woodworking
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, cycling
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching action movies is the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | avocado     | cabbage |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action  |
| Hobby           | woodworking         | camping     |
| Sport     | snowboarding   | cycling    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: tulip, azalea
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, brazilian
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
2. the brazilian is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the person who growstulip is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Flower    | azalea     | tulip |
| Job         | entrepreneur | accountant    |
| Nationality         | argentine         | brazilian        |
| Transport   | bike         | helicopter    |

