.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: drawing, magic-tricks
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian
2 different pets are kept: cat, horse
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, tiparillo
1. the tiparillo-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the egyptian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the dutch##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Hobby           | magic-tricks | drawing    |
| Nationality   | dutch       | egyptian |
| Pet           | cat         | horse    |
| Cigar         | alhambra    | tiparillo   |

